https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qxUMJazwNUBpMfc0qEnWrzqcoOG.jpg A noble prostitute is found dead in the toilet of a trendy club. Actually a normal case for Chief Inspector Lukas Laim - he would not know this woman intimately. In addition, the case gets an unexpected twist: Laim and his assistant Tim Berners encounter in the customer file of the victim on the top managers of a pharmaceutical company. Suddenly the sexual offense becomes a serious case of white-collar crime. Die Tote ohne Alibi
